name: Firefox & Chrome Add-ons
body:
## Password Manager
New most powerful tool to control your passwords.  
Based on [Parole Manager](http://parolemanager.com/).

## Map Switcher
View current point of interest on different online maps services.  
Supported services:
* [Yandex Maps](https://maps.yandex.ru/)
* [Google Maps](https://www.google.ru/maps/)
* [OpenStreetMap](http://www.openstreetmap.org/)
